  "texts": [
    "Both containerization and orchestration allow one to set up IAM rules according to their needs.",
    "Even so, policies that only experience certain events cannot detect new kinds of threats.",
    "Agents operating without supervision use the knowledge of behavior and risks to frequently block possible security breaches.",
    "Policy CI/CD Bottlenecks Cloud-Native IAM Serverless IAMAccording to Ayebo (2017), serverless architecture helps reduce the amount of work in DevOps management.",
    "Serverless functions operate fast, though they frequently use roles that allow too many actions."
